{"tid":504882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得紅墈 美味佳 完全被吹大左?","createTime":"2017-12-20T13:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T14:41:21.000Z","uid":40757,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4194a2c942ad20adc7691ebbc54d65631991f0e","tid":504882,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"今日晏畫班朋友話去食美味佳，咁小妹之前都食過一次，印象中真係麻麻，對比起其他人吹捧到天上有地下無咁，我覺得完全係overrated 。<br />\n<br />\n咁今日就叫左一大堆野食，一個字，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚鹹！！！屌你老母！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母孜然粉同辣粉重手到仆街，根本冇一樣既係唔撚鹹！！！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母一擺落口就已經feel到果陣鹹味，乸撚住成個口腔，再吞落去，不得了啦，成個食道都係乸到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n肉就又鹹又乾，出面鹹到仆街，但中間又乜味都冇之餘韌過阿婆啲肉。<br />\n菜呢就得個鹹字，究竟我係食緊菜定係食緊孜然粉？<br />\n<br />\n台灣夜市街邊燒烤檔都已經算重手架啦，估唔到你老母間美味街重手到仆街，中午食完到依家啲口水keep住狂流，灌撚左幾Ｌ水都仲係覺得個口好乾好乸！<br />\n<br />\n仆你班埋大仔，日撚日吹奏美味佳呢間垃圾！<br />\n<br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b866b89e5739853fe8637e6eddf101843fa3a9","tid":504882,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"食開屎班負皮撚出黎討論"},{"pid":"d925005b5824ac7fcb19ab7188437f1a7966ae8e","tid":504882,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，岩岩仲嘔緊啲孜然粉味出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c886faee5f47e311e078c9dad5d361557f4b6fc2","tid":504882,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"平民質素,冇乜特別,食過1次冇再食"},{"pid":"315589922500db521fbd7e83502366c5502476a7","tid":504882,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"又LOOP"},{"pid":"bb5c35d7a0f0ad50a0f6bfb639e3b2a5b9a51c3f","tid":504882,"uid":81075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"同kon u仔吹奏新興同出一轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f8606826c4661c3a98d4f670f3a0cc44bb2935","tid":504882,"uid":134825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"車子麵 先係精髓"},{"pid":"b946151fd5ed481ac9d9ece3cf227238c4026724","tid":504882,"uid":134825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車子麵 先係精髓</blockquote><br />\n車仔麵"},{"pid":"5af02ed916f9f7dfb196b3d542307cfa38090477","tid":504882,"uid":90166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"係平ja ma"},{"pid":"53a2a707e53f45d276b785a89094feefaf4a97e4","tid":504882,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"等得耐, 又唔好味, 又唔算平"},{"pid":"5c059cef6430e2317b53accc80b55c29a1ae5669","tid":504882,"uid":9466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"賣人情味啫肥婆佳"},{"pid":"a4ae18f6b0e3680b2e1146deb0d3f5cda98f67ee","tid":504882,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"食過幾次無你咁誇張，我覺得唔錯但無其他人講到咁正，同埋我唔食辣所以無咁多粉，反而我幾鍾意食車仔麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b662cbcf993ba702b666d65a7540c07fb03066db","tid":504882,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"肥婆燒雞不知幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c6a4e3f8db4b481fe410c2072a8cc88a066781","tid":504882,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"隔幾個舖位轉角位間串燒鋪好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bd42aa253b710aca0842ae60172ddfc23bfa0c","tid":504882,"uid":74402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣人情味啫肥婆佳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥婆雞絕對係埋大仔嘅集體回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}